.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, engineer, electrician, mechanic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, march, july, december
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the mechanic is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
5. the pilot is the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the pilot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Job   | electrician   | engineer         | mechanic   | pilot    |
| Birthday         | march | december | july | june |

