.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, craftsman, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, pakistani, japanese
1. the futuristic house is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the art-deco house##7
2. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
3. the futuristic house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the farmhouse house##7
4. the craftsman house is not to the left of the japanese##8
5. the japanese is somewhere between the art-deco house and the colombian##7
6. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
7. the colombian is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| House   | art-deco   | craftsman | futuristic | farmhouse    |
| Nationality         | nigerian | japanese   | pakistani   | colombian |

