.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, helicopter, subway
City: marseilles, venice, colone, berlin
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
6. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
7. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Transport          | subway | airplane | skateboard  | helicopter |
| City   | venice   | berlin         | colone | marseilles |

