.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, pakistani, german, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, van, train
1. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the pakistani##8
2. the person driving the train is somewhere between the egyptian and the person driving the van##7
3. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
4. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
5. the person driving the train is not to the left of the pakistani##8
6. the american is on the left or right of the german##3
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the american is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani      | german | american | egyptian   |
| Transport      | skateboard | van | train  | snowmobile |

