.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, frog, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, september, november, october
1. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the lizard##7
5. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the frog##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Pet     | lizard | frog | turtle | hedgehog     |
| Birthday   | december   | november        | october          | september |

