.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, cherry, cabbage, lime
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, rat, pony
1. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating lime and the owner of the dog##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
4. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
5. the owner of the hamster is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person eating cabbage is not the owner of the rat##6
7. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person eating cabbage##8
8. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | lime   | pomegranate | cabbage | cherry |
| Pet     | pony | hamster       | dog  | rat    |

