3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | cola      | sprite   | hot-chocolate  |
| Flower   | tulip    | balloon-flower | daisy | daffodil |

