.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rat, fish, mouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, funk, gospel, ambient
1. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
2. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
3. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
4. the fan of reggae is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the fish is between the fan of ambient and the fan of gospel##2
6. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet    | rat        | mouse | fish      | hamster    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | gospel   | funk | ambient |

