3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the thai##1
4. the indian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the spanish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the thai##7
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the thai##3
8. the spanish is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | spanish | thai         | indonesian    | indian       |
