.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, pink, lilac, chestnut
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, frog, bird
1. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
2. the person who likes chestnut is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
4. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes chestnut and the owner of the frog##2
5. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color   | ebony     | pink | chestnut        | lilac       |
| Pet      | frog | goldfish  | mouse | bird |

