.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go, poker
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, photography, sudoku, gardening
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 2. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing go##8
 3. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
10. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Game          | monopoly    | go | canasta | poker |
| Hobby   | dancing | gardening  | sudoku     | photography    |

