.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, cola, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, argentine, canadian
1. the polish is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
2. the polish is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
3. the argentine is not to the right of the polish##8
4. the person drinking cola is not the canadian##6
5. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the canadian##8
6. the german is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the canadian##1
8. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage           | cola | milk | coffee | iced-tea   |
| Nationality   | argentine       | canadian      | polish    | german |

