.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
City: hamburg, prague, berlin, paris
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, snooker, billiard
1. the person traveling to berlin is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is not to the left of the person playing go##8
3. the person playing go is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
6. the person traveling to prague is between the person playing go and the person traveling to paris##2
7. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City    | paris        | prague | hamburg | berlin |
| Game   | billiard | snooker | go   | mah-jongg    |

