.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, basketball, snowboarding, surfing
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, ebony, green
1. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person who likes ebony##6
2. the person who likes ebony is not to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
3. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is surfing##7
4. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
5. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
6. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
7. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person who likes green##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Sport         | parkour  | surfing | basketball  | snowboarding  |
| Color   | fuchsia | grey   | green | ebony |

