.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
City: venice, edinburgh, marseilles, miami
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, kiwi, radish, papaya
1. the person eating kiwi is not the person traveling to venice##6
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
4. the person traveling to marseilles is the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person eating raspberry##7
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person eating radish is between the person eating papaya and the person traveling to marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| City         | edinburgh    | miami | venice | marseilles |
| Food   | kiwi | papaya      | radish     | raspberry     |

 